item.immersive_aircraft.rotary_cannon.de: Bangalad degdeg ah oo u shaqeysa buundo.
item.immersive_aircraft.bomb_bay.descrip: Dhulka TNT, ma burburin karto blocks laakiin dhaawac culus bay u geysaneysaa.
item.immersive_aircraft.telescope.descri: Nooc ka mid ah muusiga leh.
item.immersive_aircraft.heavy_crossbow.d: Crossbow culus oo leh xoog badan, wuxuu u baahan yahay fallaadho.
item.immersive_aircraft.airship.descript: Airships may not be the fastest vehicle, but they sure are easy to maneuver.
item.immersive_aircraft.cargo_airship.de: Gaabis ah oo shidaal badan cunaya laakiin qaada kayd buuxa.
item.immersive_aircraft.warship.descript: Fortress duulaya, gaabis ah balse si xoogan u hubeysan.
item.immersive_aircraft.biplane.descript: Degdeg ah oo lagu kalsoonaan karo. Hubi in shaygaaga duulimaadku uu ku filan yahay.
item.immersive_aircraft.gyrodyne.descrip: Who needs an engine if one could power the aircraft with pure brawn? Give it a good push and off it flies!
item.immersive_aircraft.quadrocopter.des: A masterwork of engineering! 4 rotors strapped to some bamboo. Perfect for building, and that's about it.
item.immersive_aircraft.bamboo_hopper.de: Diyaarad weyn oo leh saddex kursi iyo pontoons si ammaan ah loogu dego biyaha.
immersive_aircraft.gyrodyne_target_reach: Xawaaraha rotorka ugu yar la gaadhay, diyaar u ah qaadista!
immersive_aircraft.tried_dismount: Mar kale riix si aad uga booddo!
immersive_aircraft.fuel.low: Waxaad ku dhowdahay inaad ka dhammaatid shidaalka!
immersive_aircraft.fat.out: Waxaad aad u gaajoon tahay inaad duusho!
option.immersive_aircraft.useThirdPerson: Hadafkoodu waa kamarada qofka saddexaad diyaarada.
option.immersive_aircraft.windThunderWea: Dabayl dheeraad ah marka thunderka dhaco.
option.immersive_aircraft.useCustomKeybi: Isticmaal keydyo badan, waxay burburiyaan qaar ka mid ah mods.
option.immersive_aircraft.showHotbarEngi: Muuji kabka matooriga ee over hotbar.
option.immersive_aircraft.enableCrashBlo: Fur qarax wax u dhimi kara.
option.immersive_aircraft.crashDamage: Waxyeeleeya ciyaaryahanka markii uu shil galo.
option.immersive_aircraft.preventKillThr: Ma dilayo ciyaaryahanka haddii uu shil galo.
option.immersive_aircraft.damagePerHealt: Qiimayaasha sare waxay ka dhigayaan diyaaraduhu inay noqdaan kuwo adkeysi leh.

option.immersive_aircraft.regenerateHeal: Si otomaatig ah ayaa caafimaadka dib u soo noqoshada markasta oo tick la siiyo, si u eg dhaqanka vanilla.
